Digits on Keyboard

key	scan code

0	48
1	49
2	50
3	51
4	52
5	53
6	54
7	55
8	56
9	57

Keyboard scan codes for digits
on the keyboard are different from the
scan codes for digits on the number pad.
However they are the same as the
ASCII Character Code decimal value.


Shift Digits         see punctuation

key	scan code

)	48 Shift
!	49 Shift
@	50 Shift
#	51 Shift
$	52 Shift
%	53 Shift
^	54 Shift
&	55 Shift
* 	56 Shift
(	57 Shift

Digits on Number Pad - Num Lock on

key	scan code

0 	96
1	97
2	98
3	99
4	100
5	101
6	102
7	103
8	104
9	105

Keyboard scan codes for digits
on the number pad are different from the
scan codes for digits on the keyboard

Pressing the shift key with the number lock on
turns off the num lock while the shift key is held
down, so pressing shift + 1 on the number
pad w/ NumLock on is the same as "End" below.

Keys on Num Pad - Num Lock off

key	scan code

5 	12
PgUp	33
PgDn	34
End	35
Home	36
Left Arrow	37
Up Arrow	38
Right Arrow	39
Down Arrow	40
Ins	45
Del	46

Punctuation
key	scan code

)	48 Shift
!	49 Shift
@	50 Shift
#	51 Shift
$	52 Shift
%	53 Shift
^	54 Shift
&	55 Shift
* 	56 Shift
(	57 Shift
* on Num Pad	106
+ on Num Pad	107
- on Num Pad	109
. on Num Pad	110
/ on Num Pad	111
[ 	219
(CHAVES DO COMENTARIO DO DELPHI - A QUE ABRE) 	219 Shift
] 	221
(CHAVES DO COMENTARIO DO DELPHI - AQUE FECHA)	221 Shift
| Pipe	220 Shift
\ 	220
; 	186
: 	186 Shift
= 	187
+ on Keyboard	187 Shift
, 	188
< 	188 Shift
- 	189
_ Underscore	189 Shift
. on Keyboard	190
> 	190 Shift
/ on Keyboard	191
? 	191 Shift

` Reverse Quote	192
~ 	192 Shift
\ 	220
' Single Quote	222
" 	222 Shift

Non Printable Characters
Backspace	8
Tab	9
5 on Num Pad w/ Num Lock off	12
Enter (carriage return)	13
Shift only	16
Ctrl only	17
Alt only	18
Pause / Break 	19
Caps Lock	20
Escape	27
Space Bar	32
Page Up	33
Page Down	34
End	35
Home	36
Left Arrow	37
Up Arrow	38
Right Arrow	39
Down Arrow	40
Print Scrn 	44
Insert	45
Delete	46
Start Menu But	92
Popup Menu Key	93
Num Lock 	144
Scroll Lock 	145

Function Keys
key	scan code

